1
00:00:07,665 --> 00:00:09,025
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

2
00:01:40,345 --> 00:01:42,945
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
‎QUEEN CHU‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

3
00:01:46,985 --> 00:01:49,345
I had calculated every move,

4
00:01:50,705 --> 00:01:53,225
yet the one I held dearest
threw it all into ruin.

5
00:01:53,825 --> 00:01:55,305
Had she not interfered,

6
00:01:55,385 --> 00:01:56,985
we'd never have endured such indignity.

7
00:01:58,825 --> 00:01:59,665
No.

8
00:02:01,105 --> 00:02:02,545
I should thank her

9
00:02:04,425 --> 00:02:06,425
for making one thing clear.

10
00:02:08,265 --> 00:02:10,105
Even the most masterful stratagem

11
00:02:10,945 --> 00:02:13,825
cannot withstand a sudden turn of fortune.

12
00:02:16,625 --> 00:02:18,905
Just like this game,

13
00:02:18,985 --> 00:02:20,985
I thought victory was all but assured,

14
00:02:21,065 --> 00:02:22,585
and yet I forgot

15
00:02:23,345 --> 00:02:24,505
that the opponent

16
00:02:25,425 --> 00:02:27,585
does not always play by your script.

17
00:02:29,665 --> 00:02:33,465
I had accounted for everyone, except her.

18
00:02:34,785 --> 00:02:36,545
Who would have thought

19
00:02:36,625 --> 00:02:40,025
that the little girl
who once wept in public

20
00:02:40,665 --> 00:02:45,305
would dare to take the pieces in hand
amid such chaos?

21
00:02:48,745 --> 00:02:51,545
But one such mistake

22
00:02:52,385 --> 00:02:53,745
is all it takes.

23
00:03:18,385 --> 00:03:21,265
Your Majesty, please accept the offering.

24
00:03:23,505 --> 00:03:27,265
The Divine Bird descends to the shrine

25
00:03:27,865 --> 00:03:31,785
as ancestral might protects the land.

26
00:03:32,625 --> 00:03:36,225
The divine aura soars
like swirling clouds,

27
00:03:37,385 --> 00:03:41,745
bestowing grace to nourish the realm.

28
00:03:54,025 --> 00:03:55,505
Chu Zhao has put Deng Yi and Xie Yanfang

29
00:03:55,585 --> 00:03:57,545
in charge of all ancestral rites,

30
00:03:57,625 --> 00:03:59,225
even the shamans' invocations included.

31
00:03:59,305 --> 00:04:01,145
Will this compromise our plan?

32
00:04:01,225 --> 00:04:02,385
Tomorrow,

33
00:04:02,465 --> 00:04:04,425
once the herbs are lit,

34
00:04:05,785 --> 00:04:07,705
Xiao Yu, standing nearest to the censer,

35
00:04:08,665 --> 00:04:09,945
will inhale

36
00:04:13,345 --> 00:04:14,665
the poisoned smoke.

37
00:04:15,705 --> 00:04:18,504
She will surely guard
against every possibility.

38
00:04:19,465 --> 00:04:20,465
Yet

39
00:04:21,425 --> 00:04:23,025
once the smoke rises,

40
00:04:24,985 --> 00:04:26,985
her days as Grand Princess

41
00:04:28,865 --> 00:04:30,305
are over.

42
00:04:32,305 --> 00:04:33,705
What's wrong?

43
00:04:34,785 --> 00:04:35,865
Yu.

44
00:04:37,505 --> 00:04:39,545
Yu.

45
00:04:39,625 --> 00:04:41,585
Yu. Yu!

46
00:04:41,665 --> 00:04:42,505
Are you alright?

47
00:04:42,585 --> 00:04:43,825
-Your Majesty. Your Majesty.
-Yu.

48
00:04:43,905 --> 00:04:45,145
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

49
00:04:45,225 --> 00:04:46,785
Wake up. Yu.

50
00:04:48,465 --> 00:04:52,385
Dark omens shadow the throne
as the Grand Princess's fate

51
00:04:52,465 --> 00:04:55,465
-Yu.
-collides with the Emperor's.

52
00:04:55,545 --> 00:04:57,425
-Wake up.
-It is as if the heavens

53
00:04:57,505 --> 00:04:59,665
-What happened to you?
-seek to sever the imperial lifeline!

54
00:05:00,265 --> 00:05:02,585
The Grand Princess has plotted
against His Majesty.

55
00:05:02,665 --> 00:05:03,705
Seize her at once!

56
00:05:08,065 --> 00:05:11,065
Whoever dares to touch Her Highness
answers to my blade.

57
00:05:11,145 --> 00:05:14,345
How insolent you are
to draw steel before His Majesty!

58
00:05:15,385 --> 00:05:16,665
None shall presume!

59
00:05:17,385 --> 00:05:20,225
Summon the Imperial Physician
to tend to His Majesty.

60
00:05:21,225 --> 00:05:22,265
Seal the palace gates.

61
00:05:22,345 --> 00:05:25,145
None shall leave without express command.

62
00:06:01,945 --> 00:06:04,385
Mr. Deng, please forgive me.

63
00:06:04,465 --> 00:06:07,145
His Majesty's pulse shows no irregularity.

64
00:06:07,225 --> 00:06:09,345
Then why does he remain unconscious?

65
00:06:09,425 --> 00:06:11,185
I cannot find the cause.

66
00:06:11,785 --> 00:06:12,825
But His Majesty's condition,

67
00:06:12,905 --> 00:06:15,585
falling unconscious
after inhaling the smoke,

68
00:06:15,665 --> 00:06:18,145
is strikingly similar
to the Crown Prince's poisoning.

69
00:06:18,225 --> 00:06:19,385
Have you identified the toxin?

70
00:06:19,465 --> 00:06:22,265
The Crown Prince's death
was never truly probed in time,

71
00:06:22,345 --> 00:06:24,025
so the source remains a mystery.

72
00:06:24,105 --> 00:06:26,065
-Keep digging.
-Yes.

73
00:06:29,945 --> 00:06:31,385
What should we do?

74
00:06:31,465 --> 00:06:35,985
Everyone involved in the poisoning
is right here.

75
00:06:38,105 --> 00:06:40,265
Why not ask them outright?

76
00:06:45,625 --> 00:06:46,505
How is His Majesty?

77
00:06:53,305 --> 00:06:54,665
What is the condition? I must go in.

78
00:06:54,745 --> 00:06:56,545
His Majesty is being attended to.

79
00:06:56,625 --> 00:06:57,905
No one is permitted to enter.

80
00:06:58,505 --> 00:06:59,265
Your Highness.

81
00:06:59,345 --> 00:07:03,265
By law, the implicated
must be held for questioning.

82
00:07:03,345 --> 00:07:05,425
Leaving your palace unbidden now

83
00:07:05,505 --> 00:07:08,505
will only make things harder to resolve.

84
00:07:09,385 --> 00:07:10,545
It wasn't me.

85
00:07:13,225 --> 00:07:14,385
What has become of Yu?

86
00:07:19,665 --> 00:07:21,265
He has yet to awaken.

87
00:07:21,345 --> 00:07:23,705
Acupuncture and herbs
have been administered.

88
00:07:26,265 --> 00:07:29,065
-What happened?
-Yet when His Majesty was poisoned,

89
00:07:30,025 --> 00:07:32,985
you were the only one by his side.

90
00:07:33,065 --> 00:07:34,105
Zhao.

91
00:07:38,505 --> 00:07:39,665
The Imperial Physician said

92
00:07:40,385 --> 00:07:43,985
his symptoms are identical
to those of his father.

93
00:07:45,225 --> 00:07:46,225
Mr. Xiao,

94
00:07:46,865 --> 00:07:48,945
do you know what poison His Majesty took?

95
00:07:52,985 --> 00:07:54,505
How strange you should ask.

96
00:07:55,465 --> 00:07:59,105
Given it was the Third Prince's doing,

97
00:07:59,185 --> 00:08:00,705
how should I know?

98
00:08:01,465 --> 00:08:03,625
The shaman

99
00:08:04,665 --> 00:08:06,345
has branded her a jinx.

100
00:08:06,425 --> 00:08:08,065
I was skeptical at first.

101
00:08:08,785 --> 00:08:10,305
But with His Majesty at death's door,

102
00:08:10,385 --> 00:08:12,705
rather than pursuing the true culprit,

103
00:08:12,785 --> 00:08:14,345
you stand here questioning me?

104
00:08:15,105 --> 00:08:18,145
Xiao Xun, I am the Grand Princess,

105
00:08:18,225 --> 00:08:20,065
-not some jinx you claimed.
-Very well.

106
00:08:21,185 --> 00:08:23,825
Perhaps you find me an eyesore

107
00:08:24,505 --> 00:08:26,265
and wish to pin the blame on me

108
00:08:26,345 --> 00:08:27,425
just to have me out of the way.

109
00:08:27,505 --> 00:08:28,985
Nonsense.

110
00:08:29,065 --> 00:08:31,265
Your Highness has quite the nerve,

111
00:08:31,345 --> 00:08:34,825
pinning this atrocity on me
without any proof.

112
00:08:34,904 --> 00:08:35,904
This is outrageous.

113
00:08:35,985 --> 00:08:37,185
Your Highness is the one

114
00:08:37,985 --> 00:08:40,065
who owes an answer for this.

115
00:08:40,144 --> 00:08:42,425
The shaman has divined an ill omen.

116
00:08:42,505 --> 00:08:44,785
Your Highness ought
not to remain here any longer.

117
00:08:47,065 --> 00:08:49,145
If Your Highness has nothing to hide,

118
00:08:49,225 --> 00:08:51,145
you might as well step aside

119
00:08:51,225 --> 00:08:52,865
and let the truth run its course.

120
00:08:53,745 --> 00:08:54,865
Indeed.

121
00:08:54,945 --> 00:08:56,705
-That's right.
-Yes.

122
00:08:57,585 --> 00:08:58,425
Enough.

123
00:08:58,505 --> 00:08:59,945
Everyone, calm yourselves.

124
00:09:00,545 --> 00:09:02,105
Something is amiss here.

125
00:09:02,625 --> 00:09:04,865
It concerns the stability of the realm.

126
00:09:05,385 --> 00:09:11,385
Please remain in your palace
until the truth comes to light.

127
00:09:12,905 --> 00:09:14,465
-Someone.
-I'll do it.

128
00:09:37,905 --> 00:09:41,145
His Majesty requires rest,

129
00:09:41,225 --> 00:09:43,385
and I shall not disturb further.

130
00:09:44,145 --> 00:09:45,305
I shall depart.

131
00:09:49,385 --> 00:09:50,305
We should leave too.

132
00:09:50,385 --> 00:09:51,865
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

133
00:09:51,945 --> 00:09:53,865
His Majesty needs rest.

134
00:09:53,945 --> 00:09:56,025
What a scene.

135
00:09:58,225 --> 00:10:00,185
You seem unbothered leaving your brother

136
00:10:03,025 --> 00:10:04,705
to keep watch over her.

137
00:10:04,785 --> 00:10:06,185
If you're worried,

138
00:10:07,345 --> 00:10:09,225
you can take his place.

139
00:10:12,385 --> 00:10:13,905
That's right. It has been a while.

140
00:10:13,985 --> 00:10:15,705
When will His Majesty wake?

141
00:10:28,625 --> 00:10:31,465
Jiu, stay here and keep watch.
I will go find Yu.

142
00:10:33,225 --> 00:10:36,065
Alright. I have already briefed
the guards at his door.

143
00:10:58,265 --> 00:11:01,385
Yu, wake up. It's alright.

144
00:11:05,385 --> 00:11:07,465
Zhao, how was my performance?

145
00:11:07,545 --> 00:11:08,905
I even fooled the Imperial Physician.

146
00:11:10,305 --> 00:11:11,865
Once you have had your pastries,

147
00:11:11,945 --> 00:11:14,265
the physician will report
that you have come to.

148
00:11:14,865 --> 00:11:16,545
You must keep it up a while longer.

149
00:11:18,625 --> 00:11:19,785
I'm sorry.

150
00:11:20,785 --> 00:11:21,865
Don't be.

151
00:11:21,945 --> 00:11:23,825
We are catching the villain together.

152
00:11:23,905 --> 00:11:25,345
I can play my part.

153
00:11:28,585 --> 00:11:30,265
But if something goes wrong,

154
00:11:33,185 --> 00:11:34,185
you could be in danger.

155
00:11:35,105 --> 00:11:38,265
You risked your life
to save me among the rebels.

156
00:11:38,345 --> 00:11:40,705
I trust you will keep me safe.

157
00:11:41,505 --> 00:11:42,825
Rest easy.

158
00:11:42,905 --> 00:11:46,425
It will not be long
before I catch the culprit.

159
00:11:46,505 --> 00:11:48,065
And once this is over,

160
00:11:48,145 --> 00:11:51,025
remember to build me a grand swing.

161
00:11:57,105 --> 00:11:59,065
I promise I will.

162
00:12:03,665 --> 00:12:04,745
Your Highness.

163
00:12:04,825 --> 00:12:06,065
What is it?

164
00:12:07,185 --> 00:12:09,585
Word has come His Majesty is awake.

165
00:12:11,945 --> 00:12:12,945
Impossible.

166
00:12:14,145 --> 00:12:16,705
Golden Finch Venom has no antidote.

167
00:12:16,785 --> 00:12:17,905
How could they have cured him?

168
00:12:17,985 --> 00:12:21,745
The Imperial Physician says
the two toxins are identical.

169
00:12:21,825 --> 00:12:23,185
That poison is ours alone.

170
00:12:23,265 --> 00:12:24,985
Is it possible they'd link it to us?

171
00:12:25,945 --> 00:12:28,185
There is no hard evidence.

172
00:12:28,265 --> 00:12:29,665
Do not lose your nerve.

173
00:12:30,385 --> 00:12:32,505
Go investigate.

174
00:12:33,585 --> 00:12:35,785
The Emperor's guards
have been replaced by Xie Yanlai

175
00:12:36,585 --> 00:12:37,665
and reinforced.

176
00:12:37,745 --> 00:12:39,865
Deng Yi has ordered
that no one is to visit.

177
00:12:43,145 --> 00:12:44,425
No one?

178
00:13:09,265 --> 00:13:10,945
As his uncle,

179
00:13:11,905 --> 00:13:13,705
I should call upon him.

180
00:13:28,305 --> 00:13:32,225
Concerned for His Majesty,
I've come to pay my respects.

181
00:13:33,865 --> 00:13:35,825
Please wait. Mr. Deng ordered

182
00:13:35,905 --> 00:13:39,145
that all visitors
must first go through him.

183
00:13:39,225 --> 00:13:43,705
His Majesty and I are of the same lineage.

184
00:13:43,785 --> 00:13:45,225
Does that count for nothing here?

185
00:13:45,305 --> 00:13:48,065
It is so grave
that we have to stay on guard.

186
00:13:48,665 --> 00:13:49,665
Please understand, Your Highness.

187
00:13:49,745 --> 00:13:52,945
Against the culprit or me?

188
00:13:53,025 --> 00:13:54,705
What is it

189
00:13:55,745 --> 00:13:57,665
that has displeased you so?

190
00:13:58,545 --> 00:13:59,745
Is the medicine ready?

191
00:14:05,985 --> 00:14:07,905
Don't be so rigid.

192
00:14:07,985 --> 00:14:10,385
He is only worried about His Majesty.

193
00:14:10,985 --> 00:14:12,145
Let him through.

194
00:14:12,225 --> 00:14:13,665
-But…
-What?

195
00:14:15,065 --> 00:14:18,825
My word is just as valid as Mr. Deng's.

196
00:14:22,145 --> 00:14:23,745
There is no need for such a temper.

197
00:14:24,505 --> 00:14:26,105
They are merely following orders.

198
00:14:27,185 --> 00:14:28,225
Please follow me.

199
00:14:43,625 --> 00:14:44,505
Your Majesty.

200
00:14:48,385 --> 00:14:50,145
It has been but a few days,

201
00:14:51,545 --> 00:14:53,585
-yet you've grown so frail.
-Your Highness,

202
00:14:54,745 --> 00:14:56,185
I am afraid this is not proper.

203
00:15:03,665 --> 00:15:06,025
The poison is indeed difficult to counter.

204
00:15:06,105 --> 00:15:08,865
Fortunately, His Majesty is blessed,

205
00:15:08,945 --> 00:15:10,745
and Her Highness has found the antidote.

206
00:15:12,465 --> 00:15:14,425
The remedy is complex, however,

207
00:15:15,225 --> 00:15:18,225
and must be taken for nine days
before it takes effect.

208
00:15:20,985 --> 00:15:24,385
Then give His Majesty
the medicine at once.

209
00:15:26,705 --> 00:15:27,745
By Mr. Deng's command,

210
00:15:27,825 --> 00:15:29,865
you two lords must depart immediately.

211
00:15:30,665 --> 00:15:31,625
Presumptuous.

212
00:15:40,185 --> 00:15:41,345
I'm here to call on His Majesty.

213
00:15:41,425 --> 00:15:43,105
Who is he to interfere?

214
00:16:00,745 --> 00:16:03,825
How did you know
that the poison he used at the ritual

215
00:16:04,625 --> 00:16:06,465
was the same one
that killed the Crown Prince?

216
00:16:06,545 --> 00:16:08,985
-I didn't.
-You didn't?

217
00:16:09,585 --> 00:16:12,345
Then why did you tell him Yu had awakened?

218
00:16:13,185 --> 00:16:14,705
I was baiting him.

219
00:16:15,385 --> 00:16:20,145
Moving against Yu proves
he killed the Crown Prince, too.

220
00:16:21,545 --> 00:16:22,505
You were using

221
00:16:23,865 --> 00:16:25,265
His Majesty as bait.

222
00:16:35,145 --> 00:16:36,505
That is why I needed you

223
00:16:37,225 --> 00:16:38,785
in the shadows.

224
00:16:39,305 --> 00:16:41,065
To catch him

225
00:16:42,705 --> 00:16:44,185
red-handed

226
00:16:44,785 --> 00:16:46,545
when the time comes.

227
00:16:51,305 --> 00:16:52,705
But what if he does not come?

228
00:16:55,505 --> 00:16:56,665
Your brother will help.

229
00:17:01,745 --> 00:17:05,464
He has seen my devotion to Yu.

230
00:17:07,105 --> 00:17:08,145
He will assist me.

231
00:17:14,944 --> 00:17:16,825
Why are you so set
on sending Xiao Xun to his grave?

232
00:17:16,905 --> 00:17:18,305
Because he deserves no less.

233
00:17:23,785 --> 00:17:27,184
-If you make a mistake--
-Then ensure no such thing happens.

234
00:17:51,065 --> 00:17:53,185
Xiao Xun, what do you think you are doing?

235
00:17:57,665 --> 00:17:59,025
Yu. Yu.

236
00:17:59,625 --> 00:18:00,585
Yu.

237
00:18:02,705 --> 00:18:03,545
Yu.

238
00:18:05,785 --> 00:18:07,505
Yu. Yu.

239
00:18:08,385 --> 00:18:09,225
Yu.

240
00:18:12,465 --> 00:18:13,305
Zhao.

241
00:18:14,385 --> 00:18:15,705
I am fine.

242
00:18:16,465 --> 00:18:17,865
I just fell asleep.

243
00:18:45,785 --> 00:18:47,825
Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

244
00:18:47,905 --> 00:18:49,705
attempted to poison the Emperor.

245
00:18:49,785 --> 00:18:51,105
This crime is unforgivable.

246
00:18:54,985 --> 00:18:57,505
With nothing but bare words,

247
00:18:58,025 --> 00:19:00,665
Your Highness would charge me
with poisoning?

248
00:19:00,745 --> 00:19:01,865
What's your proof?

249
00:19:02,465 --> 00:19:04,145
Summon the Imperial Physician.
Test the medicine.

250
00:19:04,225 --> 00:19:05,865
Summon the Imperial Physician.

251
00:19:48,145 --> 00:19:52,785
Your Highness, Mr. Deng, it's non-toxic.

252
00:19:52,865 --> 00:19:54,025
Impossible.

253
00:19:54,105 --> 00:19:54,945
What…

254
00:19:55,025 --> 00:19:56,705
What's going on?

255
00:19:56,785 --> 00:20:00,225
-What on earth is going on?
-How?

256
00:20:00,305 --> 00:20:03,465
-But his Majesty is indeed poisoned.
-Right.

257
00:20:03,985 --> 00:20:04,905
Then who did it?

258
00:20:04,985 --> 00:20:06,745
I saw him do it.

259
00:20:20,105 --> 00:20:21,105
Zhao,

260
00:20:21,985 --> 00:20:25,425
your little trap

261
00:20:26,025 --> 00:20:27,745
was far too rushed.

262
00:20:27,825 --> 00:20:29,545
In that case,

263
00:20:29,625 --> 00:20:31,505
I'll prepare a gift for you.

264
00:20:32,105 --> 00:20:33,905
What? A trap?

265
00:20:33,985 --> 00:20:36,945
Golden Finch Venom has no antidote.

266
00:20:37,025 --> 00:20:40,505
And after the coup that day,

267
00:20:41,025 --> 00:20:42,745
no one ever examined

268
00:20:43,865 --> 00:20:45,745
the Crown Prince's body.

269
00:20:46,905 --> 00:20:47,905
So,

270
00:20:49,185 --> 00:20:52,305
the news must be false.

271
00:20:54,305 --> 00:20:57,625
Have the Imperial Physician
decant a calming draft

272
00:20:58,505 --> 00:20:59,865
into this vial.

273
00:21:05,705 --> 00:21:09,985
Your Highness is clearly
the prime suspect for the poisoning.

274
00:21:10,065 --> 00:21:13,145
Yet you're framing me

275
00:21:13,745 --> 00:21:15,985
for regicide.

276
00:21:16,585 --> 00:21:20,105
So, you must be certain
I tainted this tonic.

277
00:21:20,705 --> 00:21:22,185
And yet,

278
00:21:22,265 --> 00:21:25,265
you left me alone with His Majesty.

279
00:21:25,345 --> 00:21:27,745
What is your true intent?

280
00:21:27,825 --> 00:21:30,105
Have you no regard for His Majesty's life?

281
00:21:31,105 --> 00:21:33,065
-Exactly.
-Indeed.

282
00:21:33,865 --> 00:21:37,105
-It could have hurt his Majesty.
-Indeed.

283
00:21:37,185 --> 00:21:42,625
We shared a deep bond for many years.

284
00:21:43,985 --> 00:21:45,585
Even when our betrothal ended,

285
00:21:46,105 --> 00:21:50,385
I knew feelings cannot be swayed.

286
00:21:52,745 --> 00:21:55,025
Yet, to my dismay,

287
00:21:56,705 --> 00:21:57,545
you spurn

288
00:21:58,625 --> 00:22:03,465
our past and seek my very life.

289
00:22:04,225 --> 00:22:06,745
Whatever our grievances,

290
00:22:07,265 --> 00:22:10,945
you had no right to use His Majesty
as a bait to frame me.

291
00:22:11,025 --> 00:22:13,585
Such treachery is unforgivable.

292
00:22:14,185 --> 00:22:18,905
Your Highness,
how could you be so reckless?

293
00:22:19,505 --> 00:22:20,785
The Emperor's life is sacred,

294
00:22:20,865 --> 00:22:23,305
not a pawn for you to manipulate at will.

295
00:22:23,385 --> 00:22:26,265
Should any harm befall him,
even death could not atone for your guilt.

296
00:22:26,865 --> 00:22:27,985
Indeed.

297
00:22:28,065 --> 00:22:32,105
We cannot allow such a treacherous villain
to corrupt this court.

298
00:22:32,185 --> 00:22:35,265
Bearing a title of national honor,

299
00:22:35,345 --> 00:22:37,625
yet you are devious and ruthless.

300
00:22:37,705 --> 00:22:41,265
If this goes unpunished,
where is the sanctity of our laws?

301
00:22:41,345 --> 00:22:42,865
Where is the integrity of this court?

302
00:22:43,585 --> 00:22:47,105
And how can we face the late Emperor?

303
00:22:49,145 --> 00:22:51,545
Save your breath.

304
00:22:51,625 --> 00:22:53,705
The truth is plain as day to you.
Bring her in.

305
00:22:55,425 --> 00:22:57,945
DILIGENT AND VIRTUOUS

306
00:23:15,545 --> 00:23:18,225
No wonder Yu's been haunted
in dreams lately.

307
00:23:18,305 --> 00:23:20,385
Turns out someone's been playing tricks.

308
00:23:30,985 --> 00:23:31,825
Your Majesty.

309
00:23:31,905 --> 00:23:33,345
-Zhao!
-Your Majesty. What's the matter?

310
00:23:33,425 --> 00:23:34,585
-Zhao!
-Your Majesty.

311
00:23:35,145 --> 00:23:36,025
Your Majesty.

312
00:23:37,225 --> 00:23:38,425
Yu.

313
00:23:38,505 --> 00:23:39,985
Yu. Come here.

314
00:23:40,705 --> 00:23:41,665
What's wrong?

315
00:23:42,185 --> 00:23:43,425
What happened?

316
00:23:43,505 --> 00:23:46,065
Your Highness, His Majesty has been waking
from nightmares for nights.

317
00:23:46,145 --> 00:23:48,145
Even the calming soup is all in vain.

318
00:23:49,465 --> 00:23:51,385
Zhao, I'm scared.

319
00:24:01,345 --> 00:24:02,585
It's no nightmare.

320
00:24:05,545 --> 00:24:07,265
Any new dishes on his table lately?

321
00:24:07,345 --> 00:24:09,705
Or any new ornaments placed here?

322
00:24:09,785 --> 00:24:10,665
The food is the same.

323
00:24:10,745 --> 00:24:12,825
But many tributes
and new pieces have been brought in.

324
00:24:12,905 --> 00:24:14,265
-Check them.
-Yes.

325
00:24:21,065 --> 00:24:22,305
There, there.

326
00:24:22,385 --> 00:24:24,025
I'm here.

327
00:24:26,785 --> 00:24:29,545
I saw candles flickering within,
shadows rushing about.

328
00:24:29,625 --> 00:24:30,985
What has happened?

329
00:24:31,065 --> 00:24:33,745
The air reeks of foul play.

330
00:24:44,345 --> 00:24:45,865
This incense…

331
00:24:53,865 --> 00:24:54,705
Let me.

332
00:25:10,585 --> 00:25:12,265
Calming incense

333
00:25:13,225 --> 00:25:14,305
should be fine as dust,

334
00:25:14,905 --> 00:25:15,865
completely pure.

335
00:25:16,785 --> 00:25:20,985
Yet this is laced with grit.

336
00:25:21,065 --> 00:25:24,385
It seems someone
is trying to poison the air.

337
00:25:25,265 --> 00:25:27,705
The toxins vanish with the smoke,

338
00:25:27,785 --> 00:25:29,385
destroying the evidence as it burns.

339
00:25:30,545 --> 00:25:35,065
This is the same way that killed
the Crown Prince.

340
00:25:36,825 --> 00:25:37,905
-Xiao Xun.
-Xiao Xun.

341
00:25:40,585 --> 00:25:42,505
We should find the traitor now.

342
00:25:45,185 --> 00:25:46,025
No.

343
00:25:47,305 --> 00:25:48,825
Don't alert them.

344
00:25:50,785 --> 00:25:54,705
To think he could reach Yu so easily.

345
00:25:54,785 --> 00:25:55,945
The mole will be hard to find.

346
00:25:58,385 --> 00:26:00,585
Yu, I have an idea.

347
00:26:01,345 --> 00:26:03,225
Since they're disturbing your dreams,

348
00:26:03,305 --> 00:26:06,305
let's play along and draw them out.

349
00:26:06,385 --> 00:26:07,225
Scared?

350
00:26:07,305 --> 00:26:09,985
Not with you two here.

351
00:26:11,105 --> 00:26:12,705
Replace the incense.

352
00:26:12,785 --> 00:26:14,785
The Chenxiang incense was too strong.

353
00:26:14,865 --> 00:26:17,865
Change it to a blend
with Fuling and Yuanzhi.

354
00:26:18,465 --> 00:26:19,585
At once, Your Highness.

355
00:26:20,945 --> 00:26:23,865
I've replaced the incense
with Golden Finch Venom.

356
00:26:24,385 --> 00:26:27,905
I knew you wouldn't leave this matter be.

357
00:26:29,905 --> 00:26:32,945
So, you proposed the sacrifice
in court again.

358
00:26:33,025 --> 00:26:35,705
I have something to report.

359
00:26:35,785 --> 00:26:39,545
You were certain
Yu would mention the nightmares.

360
00:26:40,145 --> 00:26:41,345
So I played along

361
00:26:42,545 --> 00:26:44,865
with your little show at the ritual,

362
00:26:46,225 --> 00:26:47,665
to lure you into it.

363
00:26:53,825 --> 00:26:55,585
You poisoned the Chenxiang incense too,

364
00:26:55,665 --> 00:26:57,425
didn't you?

365
00:26:58,705 --> 00:27:01,065
Who is the mastermind behind this?

366
00:27:01,145 --> 00:27:02,745
His Highness

367
00:27:03,705 --> 00:27:06,305
ordered me to dispose of the ash.

368
00:27:06,385 --> 00:27:08,385
I truly know nothing.

369
00:27:10,065 --> 00:27:11,225
Do you think the ash

370
00:27:11,305 --> 00:27:13,345
and a maid's testimony

371
00:27:14,105 --> 00:27:16,065
is enough to pin this on me?

372
00:27:16,665 --> 00:27:17,705
Proof?

373
00:27:19,305 --> 00:27:20,825
Without it,

374
00:27:20,905 --> 00:27:25,865
I could also say
she was coerced into slandering me.

375
00:27:43,705 --> 00:27:46,305
Does this face look familiar?

376
00:27:46,385 --> 00:27:48,105
He's from the Office
of the Great Supplicator.

377
00:27:49,265 --> 00:27:50,785
Before the ritual,

378
00:27:51,385 --> 00:27:55,705
I found that the attendant
preparing the herb wreath

379
00:27:56,225 --> 00:27:57,505
was an impostor.

380
00:27:58,225 --> 00:28:02,025
I intercepted him just in time and found

381
00:28:02,785 --> 00:28:04,465
a few trinkets on him.

382
00:28:27,265 --> 00:28:28,585
Who sent you?

383
00:28:32,905 --> 00:28:35,665
Speak. Who is your master?

384
00:28:40,825 --> 00:28:42,185
Talk.

385
00:28:43,625 --> 00:28:45,305
Who ordered this?

386
00:28:48,185 --> 00:28:49,545
Zhao, watch out!

387
00:28:56,145 --> 00:28:57,225
-Yanlai!
-Your Highness!

388
00:28:57,305 --> 00:28:58,945
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness!

389
00:29:03,825 --> 00:29:05,065
What?

390
00:29:31,505 --> 00:29:32,425
What?

391
00:29:32,505 --> 00:29:34,985
Drawing a blade before the throne.
Insolent fool.

392
00:29:37,225 --> 00:29:38,625
Did you order this?

393
00:29:44,505 --> 00:29:45,785
Overstepping?

394
00:29:46,665 --> 00:29:47,865
Giving orders and drawing swords

395
00:29:49,185 --> 00:29:50,185
instead of His Majesty?

396
00:29:50,265 --> 00:29:53,625
Killing in the court? What? Am I next?

397
00:29:54,545 --> 00:29:57,305
You're eyeing the Crown, aren't you?

398
00:29:57,385 --> 00:29:58,825
Please hold your tongue.

399
00:29:58,905 --> 00:30:02,585
That attendant was killed on the spot.

400
00:30:03,425 --> 00:30:04,945
Dead men tell no tales.

401
00:30:05,025 --> 00:30:09,265
You all claim he was the one
who poisoned the herbs,

402
00:30:09,945 --> 00:30:11,865
yet His Majesty is clearly unharmed.

403
00:30:11,945 --> 00:30:12,945
Very well.

404
00:30:13,585 --> 00:30:14,945
If so,

405
00:30:15,025 --> 00:30:19,025
then why did His Majesty
feign poisoning at the ritual

406
00:30:19,105 --> 00:30:20,945
and cause the officials to worry in vain?

407
00:30:22,745 --> 00:30:24,025
This is outrageous.

408
00:30:24,625 --> 00:30:27,745
His Majesty has been played
by a mere woman.

409
00:30:28,345 --> 00:30:30,345
What becomes of our nation's dignity?

410
00:30:30,425 --> 00:30:34,185
From the coronation
to ruling from behind the curtain,

411
00:30:34,265 --> 00:30:37,945
her ambitions to seize the throne
could not be clearer.

412
00:30:38,025 --> 00:30:41,945
-Chu Zhao's treason demands her death.
-Chu Zhao's treason demands her death.

413
00:30:42,025 --> 00:30:45,705
-Chu Zhao's treason demands her death.
-Chu Zhao's treason demands her death.

414
00:30:45,785 --> 00:30:48,105
Chu Zhao's treason…

415
00:30:48,185 --> 00:30:49,145
Silence!

416
00:30:51,585 --> 00:30:53,985
The Grand Princess has only ever sought
to ease my burdens.

417
00:30:54,065 --> 00:30:56,865
To say she has given her all
would be an understatement.

418
00:30:57,545 --> 00:30:59,785
To claim she manipulates me
from the shadows

419
00:31:00,385 --> 00:31:01,625
is sheer nonsense.

420
00:31:03,145 --> 00:31:05,945
From the day my incense
was first tampered with,

421
00:31:06,545 --> 00:31:11,465
I knew there was a traitor
plotting against me.

422
00:31:12,265 --> 00:31:14,385
Feigning the poisoning was my own idea.

423
00:31:15,265 --> 00:31:17,345
She only acted on my orders

424
00:31:17,425 --> 00:31:19,105
and has done nothing wrong.

425
00:31:19,185 --> 00:31:20,945
If any of you have objections,

426
00:31:21,025 --> 00:31:23,025
lay them before me.

427
00:31:23,105 --> 00:31:24,305
Do not trouble her.

428
00:31:24,825 --> 00:31:28,505
Your Majesty, you are still young,
unaware of the world's cruelty.

429
00:31:28,585 --> 00:31:31,705
I know who wishes me well.

430
00:31:31,785 --> 00:31:33,545
Given our blood ties,

431
00:31:33,625 --> 00:31:35,625
Uncle, for the days to come,

432
00:31:35,705 --> 00:31:37,705
rest at your estate.

433
00:31:37,785 --> 00:31:38,785
No court for now.

434
00:31:49,945 --> 00:31:52,225
Yes, Your Majesty.

435
00:31:54,105 --> 00:31:55,545
Hear my command.

436
00:31:56,065 --> 00:31:59,385
Anyone else plotting treason

437
00:31:59,465 --> 00:32:00,985
shall be executed!

438
00:32:04,345 --> 00:32:07,025
Mr. Deng, Mr. Xie, do you concur?

439
00:32:08,185 --> 00:32:09,585
Your Majesty is wise.

440
00:32:09,665 --> 00:32:12,985
We abide by your will.

441
00:32:13,585 --> 00:32:16,265
-Your Majesty is wise.
-Your Majesty is wise.

442
00:32:16,345 --> 00:32:18,905
Alright. That concludes today's matter.

443
00:32:19,425 --> 00:32:21,425
Uncle, you may leave.

444
00:33:08,865 --> 00:33:10,985
Do you find me ridiculous as well?

445
00:33:15,065 --> 00:33:16,385
You grew up in the desert,

446
00:33:17,745 --> 00:33:18,745
so you must know

447
00:33:20,345 --> 00:33:22,265
the first time a wolf tears into its prey,

448
00:33:23,465 --> 00:33:24,785
it chokes on the stench of blood.

449
00:33:27,385 --> 00:33:28,465
But it

450
00:33:29,545 --> 00:33:31,545
never lets its prey
see the tremble of its own.

451
00:33:32,745 --> 00:33:33,825
Thank you

452
00:33:35,465 --> 00:33:36,825
for saving me.

453
00:33:40,305 --> 00:33:42,825
It was you who saved me.

454
00:33:44,745 --> 00:33:45,785
Don't pick up

455
00:33:46,865 --> 00:33:48,105
a blade ever again.

456
00:33:49,865 --> 00:33:50,905
Let me.

457
00:34:09,225 --> 00:34:10,065
No.

458
00:34:16,865 --> 00:34:17,705
No.

459
00:34:20,665 --> 00:34:21,905
If you don't want

460
00:34:24,025 --> 00:34:26,105
to end up dead,

461
00:34:28,145 --> 00:34:30,225
you must strike first.

462
00:34:42,344 --> 00:34:43,344
I told you

463
00:34:44,585 --> 00:34:46,344
I only did it

464
00:34:49,425 --> 00:34:51,585
to survive.

465
00:35:03,225 --> 00:35:08,185
I fight so that more people may live!

466
00:35:09,305 --> 00:35:11,225
What does Article Three
of the regulations say?

467
00:35:13,585 --> 00:35:14,785
Suspects

468
00:35:15,785 --> 00:35:17,225
must be handed over to the court-martial.

469
00:35:17,305 --> 00:35:19,225
Why did you attack him?

470
00:35:20,025 --> 00:35:22,465
He snuck into your tent.

471
00:35:22,545 --> 00:35:23,985
He has to be a spy.

472
00:35:24,065 --> 00:35:25,385
The Army Physician told me

473
00:35:26,145 --> 00:35:28,825
he came to beg for medicine
for his sick child.

474
00:35:28,905 --> 00:35:31,425
Do you know you nearly killed
an innocent soul?

475
00:35:35,825 --> 00:35:37,585
In such tumultuous times,

476
00:35:38,145 --> 00:35:40,065
innocence is but a cloak we wear.

477
00:35:41,145 --> 00:35:43,705
General, your military achievements

478
00:35:43,785 --> 00:35:45,625
and the path you tread

479
00:35:46,385 --> 00:35:48,385
are built upon the bodies
of these "innocents".

480
00:35:48,905 --> 00:35:51,745
We both waded through rivers of blood.

481
00:35:52,505 --> 00:35:53,945
Please spare me your talk of mercy.

482
00:35:58,585 --> 00:36:01,505
Have you seen this ravaged world

483
00:36:01,585 --> 00:36:03,905
and the lives struggling
through the fires of war?

484
00:36:04,545 --> 00:36:06,105
Every campaign I fought

485
00:36:07,425 --> 00:36:09,545
was to safeguard
the hearths and homes of this land.

486
00:36:09,625 --> 00:36:12,505
But if I kill the innocent
out of mere suspicion,

487
00:36:12,585 --> 00:36:15,705
then everything I've sacrificed to protect
loses all meaning.

488
00:36:18,505 --> 00:36:20,545
He's merely a father,
desperate to save his daughter,

489
00:36:20,625 --> 00:36:22,665
who nearly died at your hand.

490
00:36:22,745 --> 00:36:24,065
Tell me.

491
00:36:24,745 --> 00:36:25,945
Is he innocent or not?

492
00:36:27,385 --> 00:36:28,425
Remember.

493
00:36:29,185 --> 00:36:30,505
Amidst this chaos,

494
00:36:31,025 --> 00:36:32,545
our hearts must hold firm.

495
00:36:33,145 --> 00:36:37,425
I wage war so that more may live!

496
00:36:52,105 --> 00:36:54,225
What was on your mind?

497
00:36:55,425 --> 00:36:56,345
I just found out

498
00:36:59,905 --> 00:37:01,465
you're just like your father.

499
00:37:05,345 --> 00:37:06,185
So dull.

500
00:37:09,825 --> 00:37:10,865
Look who's talking.

501
00:37:14,825 --> 00:37:15,665
Fine.

502
00:37:16,865 --> 00:37:18,225
Bore as he is,

503
00:37:19,345 --> 00:37:21,585
his record on the battlefield
is legendary.

504
00:37:23,545 --> 00:37:26,905
Unlike someone
who can barely hold a sword steady.

505
00:37:28,065 --> 00:37:31,825
My father taught me horseback archery
and swordsmanship himself.

506
00:37:32,745 --> 00:37:34,305
He must've been a terrible instructor.

507
00:37:40,505 --> 00:37:42,905
I had my mind set on the Capital

508
00:37:46,185 --> 00:37:47,505
and never truly applied myself.

509
00:37:59,185 --> 00:38:00,265
Let me show you.

510
00:38:04,745 --> 00:38:05,825
Ready to learn?

511
00:39:35,705 --> 00:39:36,825
Why are you sweating so much?

512
00:39:51,985 --> 00:39:52,945
Nice work.

513
00:39:54,585 --> 00:39:56,265
I learned from the best, after all.

514
00:40:05,665 --> 00:40:07,785
Your Highness. You should get some rest.

515
00:40:27,705 --> 00:40:30,265
Put this on, lest you catch a cold.

516
00:40:32,025 --> 00:40:34,585
Is this cloak so repulsive to you?

517
00:43:24,585 --> 00:43:28,505
Subtitle translation by:
